            <description><![CDATA[【🤦🏻♀️<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%AF%8F10%E4%BD%8D%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%891%E4%BD%8D%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%8A%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E6%AF%8F10%E4%BD%8D%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%891%E4%BD%8D%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%8A%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#中国每10位女性就有1位多囊患者#</span></a>】一些患者觉得，如果没有生育的需求，就可以对多囊置之不理。实际上，在你没注意时，身体的变化已经悄然发生，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%91%E4%B9%9D%E6%88%90%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%8A%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E6%9C%88%E7%BB%8F%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%91%E4%B9%9D%E6%88%90%E5%A4%9A%E5%9B%8A%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E6%9C%88%E7%BB%8F%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#近九成多囊患者月经异常#</span></a>，慢慢地，激素分泌的平衡被打破，雄激素水平迅速升高，上唇、前胸、下腹等部位体毛疯长，头发却加速脱落，痘痘频频冒头……种种异常信号，都是身体在向你疯狂示警。 <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6WXK1j1" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
